title: SSVC committee contacts over Hessisch period.

posts.content:
Just a reminder as it's the Hessisch Oldendorf / EBI / etc. etc. weeks fast approaching, please be aware that amongst the many owners making the trip, there will be quite a few of the SSVC committee venturing over into Europe.

So, if you try to call / email / message by whatever means, and you don't get a response back, please bear in mind that they're probably not ignoring you and in fact are away.
